# No Tool Branding

NEVER include text stating "made with Cursor", "built with Cursor", "generated by Cursor", or any similar attribution to the AI tool anywhere in:

- Source code, comments, or documentation
- Commit messages
- Pull/merge request titles, descriptions, or comments
- README files or changelogs
